ljgo5uKwwppVuTlM1vTM0Iq-Mu6sf9og4qN0kovOAt4sJRglglaKIbz5qFePdnkGR73bD3_j0JA7AsFyj2__Uzx1ywx8d4aOJNCJsnf2RCVBEGOYeETPzPtgFzQ3QJu4Z0MxyFwdydidY6qBQZIwFhMTqeZkOYx8slxJ8QEEYL-TJ_3DgQ-NvvQbpZg3Zlab-s2a4BzFMtqpN2DIwWumuAMHrTRcxLZrMQixnljXu8ZR98-cI7gAmbU2toHAMx6i8D3Yn3-_72f1BmrrCiVIsYH48iKJOBB5obeYn7hLO0ltAxsdeBLkNHCx5e-plQt0mw0Qh9rAEASIIUvRVfviUGAt6-s4i4H1Hj-I-uSS0MzDuu2lmq4PA1hgkGj7MCNZA4yXHtfaNoMWf_uJca_wzJyk4VT4OPP1QEW6YC60O-_hZMysB6dYmWnT3T2jD8KX09_4QFFOMxh7oT2mwyGLkT_6fmLj_SghdT3ZmZhRURFPfUX7CBBLOpH46PGZwO4sHsRC4fuyjDcZh8nOsnxFIIdFVxKrpoIo9jlrBZrekalJhkZ5L9BXhM0jBqYusqI-PVlWf7vImEiKgEpKTh_3OGhBO4iYJ714Z26g==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering class loading errors**\\n\\nI’m thinking about what happens if loadClass returns the wrong class. It could lead to a NoClassDefFoundError, especially if the class name doesn't match what's requested, like java/lang/String versus org/example. It seems that with a custom loader, the loadClass doesn't directly check the VM name, but maybe Class.forName does. It's interesting to explore how these class loading mechanisms operate in the JVM. I really want to understand this better!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_SF9uj7SRdSEnnX3uyck7cnZr|fc_0c3f87fa662cfb580169f1506a9578819cb7e9538e97fcaf30", "name": "edit", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.apache.seata/seata-all/2.1.0/src/test/java/org_apache_seata/seata_all/SpringBeanServiceInvokerTest.java", "edits": [{"oldText": "    @Test\n    void reportsUnknownConfiguredParameterTypeAfterTryingContextClassLoader() {\n        SpringBeanServiceInvoker invoker = invokerWithService(new InvocationService());\n        ServiceTaskStateImpl state = serviceTaskState(\"invocationService\", \"echo\");\n        state.setParameterTypes(List.of(\"org.example.seata.UnknownParameter\"));\n\n        EngineExecutionException exception = assertThrows(\n                EngineExecutionException.class,\n                () -> invoker.invoke(state, \"spring\"));\n\n        assertThat(exception.getMessage()).contains(\"Parameter class not found\");\n    }\n", "newText": "    @Test\n    void resolvesConfiguredParameterTypeWithContextClassLoaderFallback() throws Throwable {\n        InvocationService service = new InvocationService();\n        SpringBeanServiceInvoker invoker = invokerWithService(service);\n        ServiceTaskStateImpl state = serviceTaskState(\"invocationService\", \"echo\");\n        String contextOnlyParameterType = \"org.example.seata.ContextOnlyParameter\";\n        state.setParameterTypes(List.of(contextOnlyParameterType));\n        ClassLoader originalClassLoader = Thread.currentThread().getContextClassLoader();\n        Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(aliasingClassLoader(contextOnlyParameterType, String.class));\n\n        try {\n            Object result = invoker.invoke(state, \"spring\");\n\n            assertThat(result).isEqualTo(\"echo:spring\");\n            assertThat(service.getEchoCount()).isEqualTo(1);\n        } finally {\n            Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(originalClassLoader);\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void reportsUnknownConfiguredParameterTypeAfterTryingContextClassLoader() {\n        SpringBeanServiceInvoker invoker = invokerWithService(new InvocationService());\n        ServiceTaskStateImpl state = serviceTaskState(\"invocationService\", \"echo\");\n        state.setParameterTypes(List.of(\"org.example.seata.UnknownParameter\"));\n\n        EngineExecutionException exception = assertThrows(\n                EngineExecutionException.class,\n                () -> invoker.invoke(state, \"spring\"));\n\n        assertThat(exception.getMessage()).contains(\"Parameter class not found\");\n    }\n"}, {"oldText": "    @Test\n    void checksContextClassLoaderWhenConfiguredRetryExceptionClassIsUnknown() {\n        InvocationService service = new InvocationService();\n        SpringBeanServiceInvoker invoker = invokerWithService(service);\n        ServiceTaskStateImpl state = serviceTaskState(\"invocationService\", \"alwaysFailForUnknownRetryException\");\n        state.setRetry(List.of(retryFor(\"org.example.seata.UnknownRetryException\")));\n        ClassLoader originalClassLoader = Thread.currentThread().getContextClassLoader();\n        Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(SpringBeanServiceInvokerTest.class.getClassLoader());\n\n        try {\n            IllegalArgumentException exception = assertThrows(\n                    IllegalArgumentException.class,\n                    () -> invoker.invoke(state));\n\n            assertThat(exception.getMessage()).isEqualTo(\"unknown retry exception\");\n            assertThat(service.getUnknownRetryExceptionAttempts()).isEqualTo(1);\n        } finally {\n            Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(originalClassLoader);\n        }\n    }\n", "newText": "    @Test\n    void resolvesConfiguredRetryExceptionWithContextClassLoaderFallback() throws Throwable {\n        InvocationService service = new InvocationService();\n        SpringBeanServiceInvoker invoker = invokerWithService(service);\n        ServiceTaskStateImpl state = serviceTaskState(\"invocationService\", \"failOnceForSystemException\");\n        String contextOnlyExceptionType = \"org.example.seata.ContextOnlyRetryException\";\n        state.setRetry(List.of(retryFor(contextOnlyExceptionType)));\n        ClassLoader originalClassLoader = Thread.currentThread().getContextClassLoader();\n        Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(aliasingClassLoader(contextOnlyExceptionType, IllegalStateException.class));\n\n        try {\n            Object result = invoker.invoke(state);\n\n            assertThat(result).isEqualTo(\"retried-system\");\n            assertThat(service.getSystemExceptionAttempts()).isEqualTo(2);\n        } finally {\n            Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(originalClassLoader);\n        }\n    }\n"}, {"oldText": "    private static RetryImpl retryFor(String exceptionClassName) {\n        RetryImpl retry = new RetryImpl();\n        retry.setExceptions(List.of(exceptionClassName));\n        retry.setIntervalSeconds(0);\n        retry.setMaxAttempts(1);\n        retry.setBackoffRate(1);\n        return retry;\n    }\n", "newText": "    private static RetryImpl retryFor(String exceptionClassName) {\n        RetryImpl retry = new RetryImpl();\n        retry.setExceptions(List.of(exceptionClassName));\n        retry.setIntervalSeconds(0);\n        retry.setMaxAttempts(1);\n        retry.setBackoffRate(1);\n        return retry;\n    }\n\n    private static ClassLoader aliasingClassLoader(String aliasedName, Class<?> targetClass) {\n        return new ClassLoader(SpringBeanServiceInvokerTest.class.getClassLoader()) {\n            @Override\n            public Class<?> loadClass(String name) throws ClassNotFoundException {\n                if (aliasedName.equals(name)) {\n                    return targetClass;\n                }\n                return super.loadClass(name);\n            }\n        };\n    }\n"}]}, "partialJson": "{\"path\":\"tests/src/org.apache.seata/seata-all/2.1.0/src/test/java/org_apache_seata/seata_all/SpringBeanServiceInvokerTest.java\",\"edits\":[{\"oldText\":\"    @Test\\n    void reportsUnknownConfiguredParameterTypeAfterTryingContextClassLoader() {\\n        SpringBeanServiceInvoker invoker = invokerWithService(new InvocationService());\\n        ServiceTaskStateImpl state = serviceTaskState(\\\"invocationService\\\", \\\"echo\\\");\\n        state.setParameterTypes(List.of(\\\"org.example.seata.UnknownParameter\\\"));\\n\\n        EngineExecutionException exception = assertThrows(\\n                EngineExecutionException.class,\\n                () -> invoker.invoke(state, \\\"spring\\\"));\\n\\n        assertThat(exception.getMessage()).contains(\\\"Parameter class not found\\\");\\n    }\\n\",\"newText\":\"    @Test\\n    void resolvesConfiguredParameterTypeWithContextClassLoaderFallback() t